    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Once the chicken has had and initial 15 min, add the<strong> shredded spring greens </strong>to the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the spring greens are wilted</p>",
